---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import SiteIcon from '../components/SiteIcon.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="页面未找到" description="您访问的页面不存在。">
  <section class="container hero-panel" style="text-align:center; padding: 56px 34px;">
    <div style="display:flex; justify-content:center; margin-bottom:18px;">
      <span class="page-symbol" style="width:72px; height:72px; font-size:32px;">
        <SiteIcon name="empty" />
      </span>
    </div>
    <h1 style="margin: 0 0 12px;">404</h1>
    <p style="max-width:480px; margin:0 auto 28px; color: var(--muted); font-size: 18px;">
      这个页面飘到了深空某处，暂时找不回来了。
    </p>
    <div class="hero-actions" style="justify-content:center;">
      <a class="primary-link" href="/">返回首页</a>
      <a class="secondary-link" href="/categories/">浏览分类</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
